      "text": "Payment Gateway System",
      "fontSize": 70.27537136169519,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Payment Gateway System",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "AkkkM925aGKbnV0SU7Scv",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 23.107676265730333,
      "y": 108.87974565791171,
      "width": 684.6995849609375,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6V",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 378357560,
      "version": 494,
      "versionNonce": 1230476360,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784841150120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Requirements:\n-> Support Multiple providers (payTM, Razorpay, etc)\n-> We can easily add new gateways in future\n-> There should be a standard payment flow, with required validations\n-> Have error handling and Retries Mechanism",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Requirements:\n-> Support Multiple providers (payTM, Razorpay, etc)\n-> We can easily add new gateways in future\n-> There should be a standard payment flow, with required validations\n-> Have error handling and Retries Mechanism",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "8zMJSB-1COD26xxJiT-75",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 795.1076152305741,
      "y": 97.67974870966952,
      "width": 829.559326171875,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6W",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 18426696,
      "version": 475,
      "versionNonce": 1894632264,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784841150120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Homework (Additional Features)\n-> There can be different ways / strategies of retry mechanism (handle this in code)\n    -> Linear Retry\n    -> Exponential Back-off\n-> Try adding recurring payment flow/subscription",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Homework (Additional Features)\n-> There can be different ways / strategies of retry mechanism (handle this in code)\n    -> Linear Retry\n    -> Exponential Back-off\n-> Try adding recurring payment flow/subscription",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yHY8tZQHG77p7-nw8ROfR",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 151.34121214745028,
      "y": 335.0589168516681,
      "width": 1155.619384765625,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6X",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 924372024,
      "version": 465,
      "versionNonce": 1453662792,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784841150120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "A gateway in HLD is different , its an API Gateway\nA gateway in LLD is the gate of our application, basically for any part (or call) to go out of (or into) our application ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A gateway in HLD is different , its an API Gateway\nA gateway in LLD is the gate of our application, basically for any part (or call) to go out of (or into) our application ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
