      "updated": 1784789833591,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "This will use the template design pattern to make sure\nthat all payment transactions are always handled in the\nsame order which is a critical business requirement, which\nare initiate() -> validate() -> confirm()\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "This will use the template design pattern to make sure that all payment transactions are always handled in the same order which is a critical business requirement, which are initiate() -> validate() -> confirm()\n",
